   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 21st year, Epeiph. Petesouchos has leased to Koulos the 15 arouras formerly belonging to Kallikrates at 6 1/2 artabas of wheat (for the aroura), making 97 1/2 artabas of wheat, subject to the condition that he (Petesouchos) shall supply 15 artabas for seed and all expenses, and he (Koulos) shall sow with light crops the third part.</ab>
